headline: UBS Maintains Buy Rating on Cigna (CI) Stock
summary: On Friday, May 23, UBS analyst AJ Rice reaffirmed a “Buy” rating on The Cigna Group (NYSE:CI) with a price target of $390. Rice shared his views after a recent investor event at the Evernorth Innovation Lab, which was held together with the company’s management team.
